    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >高塔入侵者》是一款动作游戏，结合了街机的经典玩法和最现代的 Roguelite 技术。</h2>在登上高塔的过程中，您必须在每个房间的成群敌人中生存下来，在战斗、休息、购物、抢劫或测试运气之间做出选择。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169760/extras/67ae5790f2f7ae1f1cf5f88634661009.poster.avif?t=1728923117\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169760/extras/67ae5790f2f7ae1f1cf5f88634661009.webm?t=1728923117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169760/extras/67ae5790f2f7ae1f1cf5f88634661009.mp4?t=1728923117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >魔杖</h2>魔杖是《魔塔入侵者》中最重要的元素，十根魔杖中的每一根都包含五种魔法能量的不同组合： 火、电、冰、毒和黑暗五种魔法能量的不同组合。<br>为每一次 “奔跑 ”选择一根魔杖，做出正确的选择来建造最好的 “建筑”，并将你的魔法与沿途发现的强大遗迹相结合。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169760/extras/79ee3984fac962bc7451423446366437.poster.avif?t=1728923117\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169760/extras/79ee3984fac962bc7451423446366437.webm?t=1728923117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169760/extras/79ee3984fac962bc7451423446366437.mp4?t=1728923117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >塔楼</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >最后的挑战分为三层：地牢、塔楼和实验室。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >每个关卡都有一个最终 Boss 把守，一路上您必须面对他的随从和副手。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >只有击败这三个 Boss，您才能进入 “最终敌人”。获得梦寐以求的雪松魔杖后，挑战才刚刚开始。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169760/extras/fec36ac9952e9d7f3ab4a57ee43cf7c3.poster.avif?t=1728923117\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169760/extras/fec36ac9952e9d7f3ab4a57ee43cf7c3.webm?t=1728923117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169760/extras/fec36ac9952e9d7f3ab4a57ee43cf7c3.mp4?t=1728923117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不仅仅是 &quot;roguelite”</h2>无论是地图的创建，还是敌人和场景的组合，都是按程序进行的，因此每个游戏都是独一无二的。此外，场景将根据敌人的类型决定游戏的进度，从而创造出成千上万种不同的可能性。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >真正的挑战</h2>塔楼入侵者》是对要求最苛刻的玩家的挑战，胜利不是每个人都能获得的，要想战胜所有挑战，必须将技能、策略和法术知识结合起来。",
